entry.title: gdquest-demos/godot-shaders
entry.summary: A large library of free and open-source shaders for the Godot game engine. Here, you'll get 2D and 3D shaders with playable demos.

entry.title: GDQuest/godot-steering-ai-framework
entry.summary: A complete framework for Godot to create beautiful and complex AI motion. Works both in 2D and in 3D.
